{"tid":605492,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"【Viutv】 徒步L 一步四千三百公里","createTime":"2018-03-25T17:02:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-27T20:00:05.000Z","uid":110155,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"6b9177274d8a9e29c12d06d9b358ee3c08ee36a6","tid":605492,"uid":110155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T17:02:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://viu.tv/encore/journey-on-foot#journey-on-foote4yat-bo-sei-chin-saam-baak-gung-lei\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fviu.tv%2Fencore%2Fjourney-on-foot%23journey-on-foote4yat-bo-sei-chin-saam-baak-gung-lei&d=%2BhmjhRpiHp3B4TfzWDxdFtr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=3cccb95c\" target=\"_blank\">http://viu.tv/encore/journey-on-foot#journey-on-foote4yat-bo-sei-chin-saam-baak-gung-lei</a><br />\n<br />\n大家好，如果各位巴打記得的話，我上兩年(2016年)去完美國，徒步行左四千三百公里，個時有係連登出POST，都貼過唔少相，不過始終得相同少少文字，好難俾大家想像到我當時嘅生活係點。<br />\n<br />\n咁啱VIUTV最近買左個韓國紀錄片返黎，就係我行個條路(PCT)，而且仲要係同我同一年拍攝，片中有啲人我都認得，睇返真係好正，所以再同大家分享一下！<br />\n<br />\nPCT因為「狂野行」(Wild)而廣為人知，但其實Wild似係女主角的嘅個人回憶錄，而電影中嘅片段其實拍到唔太真實，但依部紀錄片係真正拍行緊人，將我地係PCT上嘅生活，真實咁拍出黎，所以大家有興趣可以去睇下。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/26/010048_d77fd49319dfd91a5233aa038b0e1db9.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F26%2F010048_d77fd49319dfd91a5233aa038b0e1db9.JPG&h=fdbeb483&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/26/010056_88871b102d7197b5c6d7a67b3fa8f75d.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F26%2F010056_88871b102d7197b5c6d7a67b3fa8f75d.JPG&h=26e3ca66&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/26/010116_349492c35c063baadba8a2313bbc86b5.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F26%2F010116_349492c35c063baadba8a2313bbc86b5.JPG&h=cffb3d01&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img s